   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Accelerate ALS research to help handicap patients</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project donate to the ALS research team based in Paris &quot;Team Boillee at ICM Pitie Salpetriere&quot; which works with other research centers in the world. The research team focuses on getting to understand the root cause of the disease to prevent its evolution. Today there is no treatment and patients loose their physical faculties as with the disease muscles stop functioning. The project also buy equipment to a handicap center &quot;Centre Kerpape&quot; the Silicon Valley of Handicap in France</narrative>
  </description>
